      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must have documented V&V test suite with regression testing and configuration management at MRL 5.",
      "rationale": "STAR-CCM+ version control and regression suite documented; however independent third-party audit of the hemolysis UDF was not completed, leaving achieved level at 3 against required 4."
