      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Benchmark solutions must confirm correct implementation of governing equations and hemolysis transport model.",
      "rationale": "Method of manufactured solutions applied to the Navier-Stokes solver; hemolysis power-law transport verified against published analytical solution for simple shear. Custom UDF verification incomplete for rotating frame source terms."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
