      "acceptanceCriteria": "Number of biological replicates must be sufficient to characterise inter-donor variability in hemolysis response; statistical power analysis required.",
      "rationale": "Factor flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5. Bench tests performed with n=3 donor blood pools; no statistical power analysis performed to justify sample size for characterising inter-donor aleatory variability. Achieved level assigned 1 pending completion of replicate study."
    },
