      "rationale": "Factor flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5. Species difference (porcine vs human blood) and haematocrit range differences between bench and COU not formally bridged. No equivalency mapping or similarity metric computed. Achieved level 1 reflects absence of formal assessment."
